Step 1 : Add the button in the homapage
<section id="order-online">
    <a href="{% url 'menu' %}"> class="order-btn">Order Online</a>
</section>

Step 2 : Style the button
.order-btn {
    background-color: #ff6600;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 18px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}
.order-btn:hover {
    background-color: #e65c00;
}

Step 3 : Ensure menu URL exists
from django.urls import path
from . import views

urlpatterns = [
    path('menu/', views.menu, name='menu'),
]
